title: The Future By Design - Jaques Fresco - Venus Project
description:
A great documentary about the way we should be living once we get over needing a government and the corp(s)e-rations devouring the planet and people with it.
As seen on Zeitgeist 2, Jaques Fresco shows common sense not too polluted with the stupidness of todays society by bringing us some real things that can be achieved easily, cheaply, super strong and beautiful buildings, vehicles and living enviroments...


...excellent stuff just at the right time to help change peoples thinking for the future of all of us as we go through 2012!

...enjoy
